      • sqlSyntaxBelow_12_2

        public static boolean sqlSyntaxBelow_12_2​(SODAUtils.SQLSyntaxLevel sqlSyntaxLevel)
        Return true if the SQL syntax is known to be below the 12.2 level. If unknown, or if known to be 12.2 or higher, returns false. This routine may be used to exclude features that can't be supported on older database labels.
